      <title>甘地担任印度议会反对党领袖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/rahul-gandhi-becomes-leader-of-opposition-in-india-s-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度反对派正准备在议会中发挥更大作用，提名拉胡尔·甘地担任重要职位，并派出自己的候选人参加议长竞选，这是一次罕见的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/rahul-gandhi-becomes-leader-of-opposition-in-india-s-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡自 2019 年以来查获 44 亿美元黑钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/singapore-seized-4-4-billion-in-dirty-money-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡在过去五年中查获了 60 亿新元（44 亿美元）与犯罪和洗钱活动有关的非法资产，其中约一半来自去年创纪录的丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/singapore-seized-4-4-billion-in-dirty-money-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:11:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国水兵手持斧头在争议海域挑起争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/china-s-ax-wielding-coast-guard-tests-limits-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在最近的南海冲突中，中国海岸警卫队挥舞着斧头，一名菲律宾水兵失去拇指，事态升级，凸显出北京方面愿意试探能将马尼拉及其在华盛顿的盟友逼到何种程度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/china-s-ax-wielding-coast-guard-tests-limits-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
